Class UnresolvedError

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Throwable
      • java.lang.Exception
        • java.lang.RuntimeException
          • com.vmware.vapi.bindings.ApiError
            • com.vmware.vapi.bindings.UnresolvedError
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Structure, Serializable

    public final class UnresolvedError
extends ApiError
    Concrete ApiError which represents a VMODL2 error that was reported but couldn't be resolved.

    This is only relevant on the client side and is used to represent errors (i.e. ErrorValue names) that are unknown for the client/stub.
